    dcterms:modified "2019-06-21T17:29:10+01:00" ;
    schema1:description "Stanley Beresford Thompson and Violet Adriana Thompson migrated from Barbados and Guyana respectively as part of the post-war rebuilding of the mother country. My father fought in the second world war and distinguished himself with medals of valour. My mother came over as a nurse as so many who were encouraged to improve their life chances and one day return back home."@en ;
    schema1:name "Geoff Thompson MBE DL"@en ;
